Package it.polimi.ingsw.Client.Model

Class Chat

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.Client.Model.Observable
it.polimi.ingsw.Client.Model.Chat
All Implemented Interfaces:
Observer
public class Chat extends Observable implements Observer
The Chat class manages both public and private chat messages within a lobby. It acts as an observable for observing changes in the chat messages. It also observes changes in the lobby users to manage private chat messages dynamically.
